7 contracts with a coordinated care organization, the coordinated care organ-
8 ization shall reimburse the provider for the cost of services provided to a
9 member of the coordinated care organization retroactively to the date that
10 the provider submitted to the Oregon Health Authority an application for
11 enrollment in the state medical assistance program that resulted in the as-
12 signment of a provider identification number.”.
